http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This innovative approach was the result of a collaboration between Samsung, the International Olympic Committee (IOC), and Olympic Broadcasting Services (OBS).\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 593, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 501, \"end\": 508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.9999995666276875, \"rank\": 4.333724354238119e-07, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}, {\"begin\": 514, \"end\": 551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 557, \"end\": 586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympic Broadcasting Services\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympics made history by holding its opening ceremony outside of a stadium for the first time.\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 699, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The highlight of the ceremony, the Parade of Nations, took place on the Seine River in the heart of Paris, with athletes from participating countries riding on boats.\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 867, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 801, \"end\": 806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999996937495339, \"rank\": 3.0625077794098737e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To capture this unique spectacle, Samsung installed over 200 Galaxy S24 Ultra devices on 85 parade boats, ensuring high-quality, real-time coverage of the athletes during their 6-kilometer journey along the Seine.\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 1082, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 903, \"end\": 910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.9999995666276875, \"rank\": 4.333724354238119e-07, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}, {\"begin\": 1076, \"end\": 1081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999887269917634, \"rank\": 1.1256238646044427e-05, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Samsung installed over 200 Galaxy S24 Ultra devices on 85 parade boats, ensuring high-quality, real-time coverage of the athletes during their 6-kilometer journey along the Seine.\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1084, \"end\": 1091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.9999995666276875, \"rank\": 4.333724354238119e-07, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}, {\"begin\": 1257, \"end\": 1262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999887269917634, \"rank\": 1.1256238646044427e-05, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Image courtesy of Samsung Electronics)  The tech giant's involvement extended beyond just broadcasting.\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1283, \"end\": 1302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.9992753868279057, \"rank\": 0.0007251386172516718, \"text\": \"Samsung Electronics\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes were provided with Galaxy Z Flip6 Olympic Edition smartphones, allowing them to capture and share their personal moments from the parade with family, friends, and fans.\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1546, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Samsung's Olympic contribution does not end with the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1548, \"end\": 1555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.9999995666276875, \"rank\": 4.333724354238119e-07, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The company revealed that Galaxy S24 Ultra devices will also be used to broadcast upcoming yacht races.\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1652, \"end\": 1655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S24_(ZVV)\", \"score\": 0.9852592205710085, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"S24\", \"types\": [\"Q728937\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S24_(ZVV)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S24_(ZVV)\"}, {\"begin\": 1656, \"end\": 1661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultraman\", \"score\": 0.614759930021834, \"rank\": 0.3170643140516216, \"text\": \"Ultra\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultraman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultraman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These smartphones will be installed on participating yachts, with the footage tr